Code of Conduct for SimDec open-source community

DOs
Be respectful to others.
We encourage you to use emojis, humor, share ideas, especially silly ones (it's where innovations commence!), and, of course, 
feel free to get insanely inspired to use SimDec and contribute to its development and spreading!

DON'ts
Do not insult or put down others. 
Remember that sexist, racist, or exclusionary jokes, harassment, sexual language, and imagery are inappropriate here.
